  <name>SegmeCam</name>
  <summary>AI-powered Linux webcam with beauty filters and background effects</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      SegmeCam is the first all-in-one AI beauty and background webcam app for Linux.
      It combines real-time selfie segmentation and face landmark detection for 
      professional-grade effects.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>AI-powered background blur and replacement</li>
      <li>468-point face landmark detection</li>
      <li>Beauty filters: skin smoothing, teeth whitening, lip enhancement</li>
      <li>Real-time controls with professional interface</li>
      <li>Virtual webcam output for Discord, OBS, Zoom, Teams</li>
      <li>GPU-accelerated performance</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Built with TensorFlow Lite, MediaPipe, OpenGL, and Dear ImGui for optimal 
      performance on Linux systems.
    </p>
  </description>
  
